  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We, we saw one room that bodies were just piled up like cordwood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I think that probably was the room that-- where Patton got sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because it-- I mean, I'm telling this from what I hear, that when he saw this one room piled up with bodies, he, he got sick to his stomach and had to leave.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think this was probably the room that he was talking about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's a picture of it there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then we, we found the, the mass graves, just great big, huge holes just scooped out of the earth with bulldozers where the bodies were thrown in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When I talk to the kids or anybody, I tell them-- give you some idea what it looked like.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Just take a piece of paper, take a pencil, and start making little [POINTING] marks all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when you get the whole paper all covered, that's a diagram of what, what these graves looked like with the bodies just thrown in all over, arms sticking up, legs sticking up, butts sticking up, heads sticking up-- all over.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Most of them naked-- some of them had clothes on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were evidence that they were trying to burn the bodies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] You, you got to remember, we're going into this place cold and not knowing anything, what is-- what's going on anywhere.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So some of this what I'm telling, I found out afterwards and relating it to what we saw.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
